      <title>美联储古尔斯比谈及 2% 通胀目标：“我们一定会实现”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/goolsbee-on-2-fed-inflation-goal-we-are-gonna-do-it-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比表示，他希望看到更多像 5 月份这样的通胀数据，以便对通胀接近美联储 2% 通胀目标感到更有信心。他在爱荷华州农业局经济峰会上发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/goolsbee-on-2-fed-inflation-goal-we-are-gonna-do-it-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 19:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息预期调整 信贷市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/credit-rallies-as-fed-rate-cut-bets-adjust-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴林高收益投资组合经理 Michael Best 和 Loomis Sayles 联席投资组合经理 Andrea DiCenso 讨论了高收益、压力和消费者问题，此前两周垃圾债券上涨，美联储略有转变。他们与 Sonali Basak 就“彭博实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/credit-rallies-as-fed-rate-cut-bets-adjust-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 19:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西基金因政策担忧增加通胀盈亏平衡押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/brazil-funds-boost-inflation-breakeven-bets-on-policy-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上个月央行在利率决议上出现分歧，巴西央行控制消费价格的承诺受到质疑，巴西对冲基金押注通胀将反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/brazil-funds-boost-inflation-breakeven-bets-on-policy-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 18:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷央行将就债券认沽风险举行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/argentine-central-bank-said-to-hold-talks-over-risks-from-puts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解谈判情况的人士透露，阿根廷央行正在与商业银行高管进行谈判，以减少主权比索债务的看跌期权积压。几天前，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 表示，看跌期权是取消外汇管制的主要障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/argentine-central-bank-said-to-hold-talks-over-risks-from-puts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 18:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果 Gecamines 威胁干预钴矿公司出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/congo-s-gecamines-threatens-to-intervene-in-sale-of-cobalt-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国国有矿业公司表示，如果新主人想要接管一项关键的采矿许可证，它需要批准对钴生产商 Chemaf Resources Ltd. 的任何收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/congo-s-gecamines-threatens-to-intervene-in-sale-of-cobalt-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 18:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道明证券的戈德伯格：降息可能会“早晚”开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/rate-cuts-could-start-sooner-td-securities-goldberg-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道明证券美国利率策略主管 Gennadiy Goldberg 表示，如果通胀前景继续向好，我们可能会很快看到降息。他与 Sonali Basak 就“彭博实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/rate-cuts-could-start-sooner-td-securities-goldberg-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 18:47:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
